title: US ambassador 'can't imagine' Biden will visit Ukraine during Europe trip: 'This is a country at war' - Fox News
content: US ambassador 'can't imagine' Biden will visit Ukraine during Europe trip: 'This is a country at war'  Fox NewsView Full Coverage on Google News
description: The U.S. ambassador to the United Nations on Sunday said there are no plans for President Biden to stop in the country this week during an expected trip to Europe for a NATO summit.
